-jun, while Lee Jun-hyuk of <em>Love Scout</em> and <em>Vigilante</em> fame plays his younger brother, Nam Gi-seok. Playing gang leader Gu Bong-san is <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/a-shop-for-killers">A Shop For Killers</a> &#39;</em> Ahn Kil-kang, while <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/bloodhounds">Bloodhounds</a></em> actor Heo Jun-ho stars as Lee Joo-woon, the leader of the rival gang Gi-seok belonged to.</p><p> Other actors expected to appear in <em>Mercy For None</em> include <em>Villains&#39;</em> Lee Beom-soo, <em>Lovers of the Red Sky&#39;s</em> Gong Myung, <em>The Trauma Code&#39;s</em> Choo Yeong-woo, <em>Mr. Plankton&#39;s</em> Jo Han-chul as well as <em>Our Blues&#39;</em> Cha Seung-won 。</p><h2> Is there a trailer for the new Netflix K-drama?</h2><p> Netflix released a “sneak peek” video clip on February 4 containing a scene lifted from <em>Mercy For None.</em>在长达两分钟的剪辑中，Nam Gi-Jun打电话给Sim Seong-Won，他隐约威胁着他。 Once he hangs up, Sim Seong-won scrambles to gather as many goons as he can at his office building, only for them to be wiped clean by Gi-jun. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Mercy For None |偷看| Netflix [ENG SUB]" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qg6tV0sG9bM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2> How to watch <em>Mercy for None</em> ?</h2><p> Netflix has yet to announce a specific premiere date for its upcoming K-drama series, <em>Mercy for None</em> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/netflix-k-drama-mercy-for-none-so-ji-sub-plot-cast-premiere-more-3834350">Here&#39;s a sneak peek at Netflix K-drama &#39;Mercy For None&#39;, starring So Ji-sub</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
